@{
    Layout = "_Layout";  // Link to the layout file
}

<div class="main-content">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="text-center my-5">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

        <div class="about-uptm-section mb-5">
            <h2 class="text-primary">About UPTM</h2>
            <p class="lead">
                Universiti Poly-Tech Malaysia (UPTM) is a distinguished higher education institution, renowned for its years of continuous growth and adaptation, which have resulted in a profound wealth of experience and expertise.
            </p>
            <p>
                At UPTM, education extends beyond academic theories, focusing on the holistic development of vital human skills, attitudes, and capabilities. Dedicated faculty members provide personalised support and guidance to help every student achieve their full potential.
            </p>
            <p>
                The university’s curriculum integrates modern technologies with business education, offering a diverse selection of innovative programs that cultivate students' skills and competencies, ensuring their success in today’s fast-paced business environment. The term “Poly-Tech” here highlights the infusion of advanced technologies into business studies, distinct from vocational or technical training.
            </p>
            <p>
                Overall, UPTM prioritises producing graduates who are not only knowledgeable and skilled but also embody professionalism, ethical integrity, and social responsibility. Through its unwavering dedication to academic excellence, UPTM empowers students to embark on fulfilling careers and make meaningful contributions to society.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title text-success">Vision</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            To establish itself as the university of choice for nurturing professionals who positively impact the nation.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title text-info">Mission</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>&#10148; To cultivate ethical, well-rounded, and balanced professionals.</li>
                            <li>&#10148; To leverage knowledge and cutting-edge technologies for the advancement of the nation.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title text-warning">Core Values</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>&#10148; Integrity</li>
                            <li>&#10148; Compassion</li>
                            <li>&#10148; Perseverance</li>
                            <li>&#10148; Respect</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title text-danger">Objectives</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>&#10148; To create opportunities for pursuing industry-recognised academic programs.</li>
                            <li>&#10148; To offer engaging and market-relevant programs that meet industry and community demands.</li>
                            <li>&#10148; To design courses that foster synergetic skills in graduates.</li>
                            <li>&#10148; To prepare graduates effectively for both local and international job markets.</li>
                            <li>&#10148; To use human resource development programs to instill societal values.</li>
                            <li>&#10148; To develop a distinguished and accountable center for excellence in research, consultation, and service delivery.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div> <!-- End of Container -->
</div>
